’t belong to those who sell policies. It will belong to those who turn insurance into opportunity.\n\n  [China Life Insurance records sharp jump in annual profit   chinadaily.com.cn](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Echinadaily%2Ecom%2Ecn%2Fa%2F202603%2F28%2FWS69c7ae0ba310d6866eb406d0%2Ehtml&urlhash=P9kl&trk=public_post_feed-article-content)\n\n  [4](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fthomas-ngeso-omeno-50b90b1b5_china-life-insurance-records-sharp-jump-in-activity-7443877107514056704-daZv&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n\n  [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fthomas-ngeso-omeno-50b90b1b5_china-life-insurance-records-sharp-jump-in-activity-7443877107514056704-daZv&trk=public_post_like-cta)   [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fthomas-ngeso-omeno-50b90b1b5_china-life-insurance-records-sharp-jump-in-activity-7443877107514056704-daZv&trk=public_post_comment-cta)\n\n  To view or add a comment, [sign in](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fthomas-ngeso-omeno-50b90b1b5_china-life-insurance-records-sharp-jump-in-activity-7443877107514056704-daZv&trk=public_post_feed-cta-banner-cta)\n* [Samantha Waite](https://au.linkedin.com/in/samanthawaitetabooeducation?trk=public_post_feed-actor-name)\n\n  Taboo Education•153 followers\n\n  + [Report this post](/uas/login?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsamanthawaitetabooeducation_new-video-why-life-insurance-keeps-appearing-activity-7445726805430505472-L7M0&trk=public_post_ellipsis-menu-semaphore-sign-in-redirect&guestReportContentType=POST&_f=guest-reporting)\n\n  NEW VIDEO: Why Life Insurance Keeps Appearing in American Murder Cases (And Why It Barely Happens Anywhere Else) WATCH: [https://lnkd.in/gkpXtfqT](https://www.linkedin.com/redir/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Flnkd%2Ein%2FgkpXtfqT&urlhash=02j4&trk=public_post-text) If you watch American true crime, you've noticed it. Life insurance keeps showing up as the motive, and the victim almost never knew the policy existed. This isn't a coincidence. It's a structural problem baked into how the US life insurance system actually works. In this video we break down exactly how someone in the US can secretly take out a life insurance policy on another person without their knowledge or consent, why there's no centralised database tracking how much coverage is being stacked on a single life across multiple insurers, and why the coroner system and the insurance industry have never been required to talk to each other. We also look at how Australia's compulsory superannuation system makes this kind of scheme significantly harder to pull off, and why \"my partner secretly insured me and then killed me for the payout\" is simply not a recognisable genre in Australian true crime. Topics covered include the insurable interest loophole, Stranger-Owned Life Insurance (STOLI), the two-year contestability period, why insurers often pay out before a conviction, and why children are not exempt from this problem. The fixes are not complicated. So why hasn't it been fixed?\n\n\n\n  [1](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsamanthawaitetabooeducation_new-video-why-life-insurance-keeps-appearing-activity-7445726805430505472-L7M0&trk=public_post_social-actions-reactions)\n\n  [Like](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsamanthawaitetabooeducation_new-video-why-life-insurance-keeps-appearing-activity-7445726805430505472-L7M0&trk=public_post_like-cta)   [Comment](https://www.linkedin.com/signup/cold-join?session_redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsamanthawaitetabooeducation_new-video-why-life-insurance-k